  "description": "A simple way to allow players to link their social media to their server profile!",
  "body": "<center>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/646b15f786975823f1a4baad\" />\n<br /><br />\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/646b160a86975823f1a4babd\" /><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/plugin/profiles/versions\"><img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/646b160a86975823f1a4bab5\" /></a><a href=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/wiki/MTProfiles/\"><img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/646b160a86975823f1a4bab3\" /></a><a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\"><img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/646b160a86975823f1a4bab1\" /></a>\n<br />\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a7b33a4601524a4b0b0d25\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a7b33d4601524a4b0b0d27\" />\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\"><img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/638a91e9aa2989386ab8ef79\" /> </a>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Full transcript</summary>\nMTProfiles\nLINK ANY SOCIAL MEDIA\nFrom all popular social medias, to even just your server's forum, all platforms are configurable!\n\nSimple interface allowing players to view each others profiles and see what is linked!\n\nFOLLOW SYSTEM\nPlayers can follow each other to keep in touch!\n\nPlayers are able to follow each other and build up lists of people\n\nLOGIN STATISTICS\nNo more arguing over who came first!\n\nLet the oldest players on your server show off with their profile\n\nPERFORMANCE\n\nAggresive caching and performance built right from the foundation of the plugin makes sure your server stays snappy.\n</details>\n</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/views/HiQ5FQASIB8mHBMQLz0GAx0dJwcrTysJIxwGHgIRJwc\" />",
